<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Test: Text-transform and bicameral scripts</title>
        <link rel="author" title="Microsoft" href="http://www.microsoft.com/" />
        <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/text.html#caps-prop" />
        <meta name="flags" content="" />
        <meta name="assert" content="The text-transform capitalizes a bicameral script." />
        <style type="text/css">
            span
            {
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Test passes if there is an upper-case letter "A" below.</p>
        <div>
            <span>&#97;</span>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>